                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for determining lithium content in lithium titanate",
                    "一种测定钛酸锂中锂含量的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a method for measuring lithium content in lithium titanate. The method comprises the following steps: weighing a lithium titanate sample to be detected, wherein the weight precision is 1.0 mg; the preparation method comprises the following steps: stirring and mixing powdery lithium titanate (Li4Ti5O12) and ferric phosphate (FePO4) in a corundum crucible by a dry method according to a ratio, dropwise adding glucose (C6H12O6) water, and stirring into a sticky paste; the preparation method comprises the following steps of: putting lithium iron phosphate (LiFePO4) and titanium dioxide (TiO2) into a microwave oven, covering the microwave oven with a cover, placing the microwave oven in the center of a microwave cavity, introducing nitrogen (99.99%) with the flow of 3-5L/min, and heating for 3-10 minutes by adopting electromagnetic waves with the frequency of 2450MHz and the power of 675W to obtain a mixed product of lithium iron phosphate (LiFePO4) and titanium dioxide (TiO2) Accurately weighing the sample, dissolving the calcined product with sulfuric acid or hydrochloric acid, and adding hydrogen peroxide which is 10% of the calcined product in dosage; filtering and separating, washing a filter cake with 20-50ml of water, transferring washing water and filtrate into a volumetric flask for constant volume, testing the lithium content through atomic absorption, and converting to obtain the lithium content of 5.81%; the test result is 0.01% different from the test result obtained by treating with aqua regia at 150 DEG C for 5 hours; the test result is 0.015% different from the test result obtained by carrying out hydrothermal reaction on concentrated hydrochloric acid and concentrated sulfuric acid in a ratio of 3: 1 at 120 DEG C for 5 hours; the test result is 0.02% different from the test result of treating aqua regia at normal pressure for 24 hours"
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种测定钛酸锂中锂含量的方法。其过程是：称取待测样钛酸锂，重量精度为1.0mg。按比例将粉末形态的钛酸锂（Li4Ti5O12）和磷酸铁（FePO4）在刚玉坩埚中干法搅拌混合，滴加葡萄糖（C6H12O6）水，搅拌成黏糊状。盖上盖置于微波腔体中央，通入流量3~5L/min的氮气（99.99%），采用2450MHz、功率675W的电磁波加热3~10min，得到磷酸铁锂（LiFePO4）和二氧化钛（TiO2）的混合产物。精确称样，先将煅烧产物通过硫酸或盐酸溶解，添加煅烧产物用量10%的双氧水。过滤分离，滤饼用20~50ml水冲洗，洗水和滤液转移到容量瓶中定容，通过原子吸收测试锂含量，换算后锂含量为5.81%；与用王水150℃处理5h的测试结果相差0.01%；与用浓盐酸：浓硫酸为3:1反应釜120℃水热5h测试结果相差0.015%；与王水常压处理24h测试结果相差0.02%。"
                }
